### InventoryService — API test collection
### Chạy: npm run seed && npm start   (server: http://localhost:3004)
### Dùng VS Code "REST Client" extension → bấm "Send Request" trên từng khối.
### Seed data: 1001 (qty 50), 1002 (qty 12), 1003 (qty 3)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3004

### 0. Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### -------------------------------------------------------------------------
### checkInventory (D5) — xem tồn kho
### -------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 1. Check item 1001 (qty 50, reserved 0)
GET {{baseUrl}}/inventory/1001/check

### 2. Check item 1003 (qty 3)
GET {{baseUrl}}/inventory/1003/check

### -------------------------------------------------------------------------
### MAIN FLOW: reserve (D11, prepare) -> commit (S9, commit)
### -------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 3. Reserve 2 units of 1001  -> quantityReserved += 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/inventory/1001/reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{ "amount": 2 }

### 4. Commit 2 units of 1001  -> quantity -= 2, reserved -= 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/inventory/1001/commit
Content-Type: application/json

{ "amount": 2 }

### -------------------------------------------------------------------------
### ALTERNATIVE FLOW (Fig 22.15a): reserve -> abort (S11 "Items Released")
### -------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 5. Reserve 5 units of 1001
POST {{baseUrl}}/inventory/1001/reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{ "amount": 5 }

### 6. Abort 5 units of 1001  -> reserved nhả về, quantity KHÔNG đổi
POST {{baseUrl}}/inventory/1001/abort
Content-Type: application/json

{ "amount": 5 }

### -------------------------------------------------------------------------
### update — nhập thêm kho
### -------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 7. Restock 1003 thêm 20 units  -> quantity += 20
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/inventory/1003
Content-Type: application/json

{ "amount": 20 }

### -------------------------------------------------------------------------
### ERROR CASES
### -------------------------------------------------------------------------

### 8. Out of stock -> 409 (reserve 100 khi 1003 chỉ có 3)
POST {{baseUrl}}/inventory/1003/reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{ "amount": 100 }

### 9. Validation -> 400 (amount không hợp lệ)
POST {{baseUrl}}/inventory/1001/reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{ "amount": 0 }

### 10. Not found -> 404 (item không tồn tại)
GET {{baseUrl}}/inventory/9999/check

### 11. Commit quá số đã reserve -> 409
POST {{baseUrl}}/inventory/1002/commit
Content-Type: application/json

{ "amount": 5 }
